===氧-15===
氧-15是氧的放射性[[同位素|同位素]]，常以{{le|氧-15水|15O-water}}的形式用于[[正电子断层扫描|正电子断层扫描]]（PET）的{{le|心肌灌注成像|Myocardial perfusion imaging}}和[[脑|脑]]成像。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Rischpler|first1=Christoph|last2=Higuchi|first2=Takahiro|last3=Nekolla|first3=Stephan G.|title=Current and Future Status of PET Myocardial Perfusion Tracers|journal=Current Cardiovascular Imaging Reports|date=22 November 2014|volume=8|issue=1|pages=333–343|doi=10.1007/s12410-014-9303-z}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Kim|first1=E. Edmund|last2=Lee|first2=Myung-Chul|last3=Inoue|first3=Tomio|last4=Wong|first4=Wai-Hoi|title=Clinical PET and PET/CT: Principles and Applications|date=2012|publisher=Springer|isbn=9781441908025|page=182|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jj9eHkn1tR0C&pg=PA182|language=en|access-date=2022-02-10|archive-date=2022-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220210142911/https://books.google.com/books?id=jj9eHkn1tR0C&pg=PA182|dead-url=no}}</ref>它有8个质子和7个中子，原子量为15.0030654 amu，[[半衰期|半衰期]]122.24秒。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/oxygen+15|title=oxygen 15 - definition of oxygen 15 by Medical dictionary|work=Medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com|access-date=2014-12-02|archive-date=2022-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220210142803/https://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/oxygen+15|dead-url=no}}</ref>氧-15可以由在[[回旋加速器|回旋加速器]]中用[[氘|氘]]轰击[[氮-14|氮-14]]而成。<ref>{{cite web|title=Production of PET Radionuclides|url=http://www.petnm.unimelb.edu.au/pet/detail/radionuc.html|publisher=Austin Hospital, Austin Health|access-date=6 December 2012|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130115012317/http://www.petnm.unimelb.edu.au/pet/detail/radionuc.html|archive-date=15 January 2013}}</ref>

氧-15和氮-13分别由[[γ射线|γ射线]]把大气中的氧-16和氮-14的一个中子轰掉而成：<ref>{{cite news|last1=Timmer|first1=John|title=Lightning strikes leave behind a radioactive cloud|url=https://arstechnica.com/science/2017/11/lightning-strikes-leave-behind-a-radioactive-cloud/|work=Ars Technica|date=25 November 2017|language=en-us|accessdate=2022-02-10|archive-date=2022-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220210141509/https://arstechnica.com/science/2017/11/lightning-strikes-leave-behind-a-radioactive-cloud/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
:<sup>16</sup>O + γ → <sup>15</sup>O + n
:<sup>14</sup>N + γ → <sup>13</sup>N + n
氧-15会以约两分钟的半衰期衰变成氮-15，并放出一个[[正电子|正电子]]。这个正电子迅速和一个电子湮灭，并产生两个能量约为511 keV的γ射线。这些低能量的γ射线只能在空气中移动90米。它和来自氮-13的正电子产生的γ射线一样只能在一分钟内左右检测到，因为<sup>15</sup>O和<sup>13</sup>N的“云”会随风飘散。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Teruaki Enoto|display-authors=etal|title=Photonuclear reactions triggered by lightning discharge|journal=Nature|volume=551|issue=7681|pages=481–484|date=Nov 23, 2017|doi=10.1038/nature24630|pmid=29168803|bibcode=2017Natur.551..481E|arxiv=1711.08044}}</ref>

